tip.text: Milo Godzilla was yummy, strawberry freeze was good. But definitely not strong enough!
The bread was amazing. Had the beef steak, medium was a little too tough for me. Brusselsprouts were not to my liking. But, fantastic service!
Play darts! Play pool! Tried the double choc stout.
The midori melon sake was yumz. The hibiki whisky was not my cup of tea... SPAM FRIES and calamari were not bad!
My fav jap place to date :) love the enoki pork skewer, sake mentai, cod fish skewer, and the salmon maki rolls!!! Never fails to leave me satisfied 😋
